ta-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Par\n                    thenopeus\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Par\n                    thenopeus\">PAR<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>THENOPEUS</span></span><br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>CONIUGI·DULCISS</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic000479_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic000479_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000479.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic000479-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>text of Salinas</span></span>; </li><li><span class=\"2\">2: <span>Gualtherus: Vegelae</span></span><br></li><li><span class=\"6\">6: <span>Gualtherus: Parthenopeus</span></span><br></li><li><span class=\"7-8\">7-8: <span>Gualtherus: dul-/cissimae</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5677-4679\">Alessandra Rocchetti</a></p>  <p>Alla memoria della sventurata Vegeia che visse ventuno anni tre mesi diciasette giorni. Partenopeo (predispose questo) per l'amatissima coniuge</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5677-4679\">Alessandra Rocchetti</a></p>  <p>In memory of the unfortunate Vegeia who lived twenty-one years three months and seventeen days. Parthenopeus (set this up) for his beloved wife</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>